c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3d85b50a2a364c22cf8ea103ca8aa2b03cc23d87","tid":442254,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9 邊有得直接比較alu<br />\nAmd夠多過nvidia啦<br />\n咪一樣唔夠抽</blockquote><br />\nTPU 個運算力強nvidia幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTPU係特別for machine learning<br />\nNV個套唔係，係通用計算"},{"pid":"cbba8f898ec912beb2af07cab5a709a69e50577b","tid":442254,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>On9 邊有得直接比較alu<br />\nAmd夠多過nvidia啦<br />\n咪一樣唔夠抽</blockquote><br />\nTPU 個運算力強nvidia幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">GTX 1080 Ti 10.6 TFLOPS</span><br />\nGoogle果粒得3TOPS<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n仲有pixel2粒IPU已經用緊，係未放API出黎"}]}